OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776280294
OL,3,CBoy, 16, arrested after 'personal
OL,4,Cdata' compromised in school cyber
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FA 16-year-old boy has been arrested by
OL,8,Fpolice investigating a cyber attack
OL,9,Ftargeting the IT system used by
OL,10,Fschools in Northern Ireland.
OL,12,FThe Education Authority (EA) "some
OL,13,Fpersonal data," it's believed, was
OL,14,Fcompromised in the attack earlier in
OL,15,FApril.
OL,17,FThe IT system, called C2K left schools
OL,18,Fand pupils unable to log into their
OL,19,Faccounts.
OL,26,@tD@^OUuD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
