FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776280294
OL,3,CBoy, 16, arrested after 'personal
OL,4,Cdata' compromised in school cyber
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FAn EA spokesperson said: "The ongoing
OL,8,Finvestigation into the recent cyber
OL,9,Fincident has now confirmed that there
OL,10,Fwas a targeted attack on a small
OL,11,Fnumber of schools which is believed to
OL,12,Fhave compromised some personal data.
OL,14,F"Our immediate priority is notifying
OL,15,Fthe individuals and schools impacted
OL,16,Fby the attack.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776280294
OL,3,CBoy, 16, arrested after 'personal
OL,4,Cdata' compromised in school cyber
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"That process is being urgently
OL,8,Fprogressed, guided by the final
OL,9,Ffindings of the investigation and
OL,10,Fadvice from the PSNI and the
OL,11,FInformation Commissioner's Office.
OL,13,F"It remains the assessment of our
OL,14,Fsystem managers that the cyber
OL,15,Fincident is contained.
OL,17,F"Additional security measures were
OL,18,Fdeployed at the beginning of this
OL,19,Fmonth on detection of the incident.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776280294
OL,3,CBoy, 16, arrested after 'personal
OL,4,Cdata' compromised in school cyber
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"Intensive work continues to ensure
OL,8,Fschools are fully reconnected to the
OL,9,FC2k system and that all impacted
OL,10,Fsystems return to normal."
OL,12,FOnline and IT systems in schools are
OL,13,Fprovided through the C2K network. The
OL,14,FEA recently apologised for the impact
OL,15,Fof the cyber attack on pupils who were
OL,16,Fpreparing for exams over the Easter
OL,17,Fbreak.
OL,19,FThe C2K system is used to support
OL,20,Fteaching of the curriculum in Northern
OL,21,FIreland.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
