PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1776280294
OL,3,CBoy, 16, arrested after 'personal
OL,4,Cdata' compromised in school cyber
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FThe PSNI said: "Detectives from the
OL,8,FPolice Service of Northern Ireland's
OL,9,Fcyber crime investigation team
OL,10,Farrested a 16-year-old male on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of offences under Sections
OL,12,F1, 2 and 3A of the Computer Misuse Act
OL,13,F1990.
OL,15,F"The male was arrested earlier today
OL,16,F(Wednesday) in the Portadown area,
OL,17,FWednesday 15 April, and has since been
OL,18,Freleased pending further enquiries.
OL,20,F"A follow-up search has taken place.
OL,26,@oD@POUwD@AOUxD@ApmxD@Kpn|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
