OL,3,CBoy, 16, arrested after 'personal
OL,4,Cdata' compromised in school cyber
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,F"The arrest forms part of an ongoing
OL,8,Finvestigation into a report received
OL,9,Fon Thursday 2 April of network
OL,10,Fintrusion activity involving the
OL,11,FEducation Authority."
